"https://www.v2ex.com/u/340244120w","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a23c/8c28/431222_mini.png?m=1563975578"},{"id":869662,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869662","replies":59,"created_ts":1659172662,"created":"17:17:42","title":"不要喷我！我发现 V2EX 的品质在下降啊","author":"v2bigbig","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2bigbig","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ddefabac739a7beb2648571c89ef72fb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":869673,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>主要是以下两个配置，pdd 和淘宝都是 ￥ 12,000 。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>MacBook Pro 14  16g RAM + 512G SSD</li>\n<li>MacBook Air M2  24G RAM + 512G SSD </li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<p>大家怎么看 m1 pro 和 m2 在性能上的差别。之前在上家公司用的 M1 Air ，个人感觉性能上没有瓶颈。</p>\n<p>个人觉得 macbook pro 14 的优势在于更强的性能和 120Hz 刷新率屏幕， 新 Air 的优势则在于轻薄的机身和续航。</p>\n<p>而我有高配 PC ，对性能没啥追求，所以更想选择新 Air ，大家怎么看捏</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869673","replies":41,"created_ts":1659178539,"created":"18:55:39","title":"同样价格选择 24g+512g 的 Air 还是 16+512 标配 pro？","author":"cogear","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cogear","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3bf7/46ac/374462_mini.png?m=1656578315"},{"id":869618,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>tbjd.store 值多少钱</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869618","replies":40,"created_ts":1659151898,"created":"11:31:38","title":"既然大伙儿都在估值域名，我也来一个 tbjd.store (淘宝京东.商城)","author":"syficy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/syficy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8f314e448884168201dd7b1f0df7fbd3?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":869663,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"有没有啥无风扇的降温方案？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869663","replies":39,"created_ts":1659173076,"created":"17:24:36","title":"最静音的笔记本降温方案是啥？","author":"ttgo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ttgo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/54a9/40cc/276192_mini.png?m=1646794004"},{"id":869651,"node":"奇思妙想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885","description":"<p>最近整理了一下电脑，然后开始整备份。</p>\n<p>备份的话，貌似最简单的办法是买几个移动硬盘？机械移动硬盘体质一般般，就怕摔一下，或者遇到品控不好的硬盘，反正总觉得不是很牢靠。SSD 更不打算考虑，整理出来的数据量大约 10T 不到，买多块大容量的 SSD 还是比较贵的。</p>\n<p>然后开始考虑买个 NAS ，其实我已经考虑很久了，组装机、品牌机的方案都考虑过，但最后还是没有选择。主要是 NAS 提供的各种功能我并不需要，我不跑虚拟机、Docker ，不需要局域网串流多媒体，我只要个牢靠的地方多保存一份数据的副本。</p>\n<p>最后花钱买了磁带（ LTO-5 ），便宜是真便宜，机房淘汰的机器 1K （免费赠送 HBA 卡），二手磁带 30 块一卷，LTO-5 磁带的非压缩容量是 1.5TB ，10 盘磁带如果完全不压缩的话可以装 15T ，才 300 块钱，比很多 Switch 游戏卡带还便宜……</p>\n<p>一家德企还提供了免费的磁带备份软件，提供一些诸如文件浏览、文件打包、增量备份之类的基本功能，个人用用足够了</p>\n<p>磁带写好后扔箱子里塞沙发底下了，增量备份的话，目测半年搞一次就行了，唯一美中不足的是，LTO-5 容量还是小了点（本想上 LTO-6 的，但是 LTO-6 机器贵了不少），然后每年要倒带一次，把磁带卷紧，算是维护吧。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869651","replies":34,"created_ts":1659167787,"created":"15:56:27","title":"最后没买 NAS，把钱花在磁带上了","author":"testcaoy7","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/testcaoy7","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e474/70a5/89326_mini.png?m=1470725674"},{"id":869665,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>之前用的腹灵 FL980 ，凯华静音粉轴。按键手感很轻，压力只有 35+-10 。久用手不累，而且非常静音。\n为了拯救肩颈，打算把公司用的 mbp 架高，用键盘。找了很多机械键盘，虽然有 mac 方案，但是 alt 按键离 cv 都比原生键盘元，感觉很不舒服。各位有什么静音、按键轻的机械键盘推荐吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869665","replies":29,"created_ts":1659174599,"created":"17:49:59","title":"有什么静音的机械键盘适合 macOS 吗？","author":"zhyf007","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhyf007","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c52c/7991/494431_mini.png?m=1658628813"},{"id":869604,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","description":"<p>如果做一个国内 sass 平台，</p>\n<p>个人有可通申请支付宝或者微信的在线支付功能嘛？</p>\n<p>如果不行，有其它付付渠道嘛？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869604","replies":28,"created_ts":1659146840,"created":"10:07:20","title":"个人做微型 sass 平台，支付问题","author":"luffy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/luffy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e555/ebe0/692_mini.png?m=1583562833"},{"id":869683,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"速娃云跑路了吗，官网都打不开。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869683","replies":24,"created_ts":1659185537,"created":"20:52:17","title":"速娃云跑路了吗","author":"n2l","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/n2l","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fc64/6dae/253420_mini.png?m=1654233814"},{"id":869593,"node":"买买买","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mmm","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_mini.png?m=1643850384","description":"<p>1.我之前在京东自营店购买了安克一个充电宝，没用几次就坏了，好像中国版的电子产品多少有点被阉割？<br/>\n2.在那些 app 或者网站能够买到美版、欧版、日版等 相对好一点的、能够正常使用的（比如电压）？我购买的东西以电子产品为主。<br/>\n3.谢谢！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869593","replies":22,"created_ts":1659142787,"created":"08:59:47","title":"安克出了 120 W 小巧充电器，在哪能够买到国外版的？","author":"xx3122","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xx3122","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d5e9fdebe90b285b558cfc24bf12685?s=24&d=retro"}]